query.description: Returns a list of alarms with severity filter set to major. The list will contain the objectFullName of each resulting alarm.
Returns a list of alarms with filter like alarmName with Equipment. The list will contain the objectFullName of each resulting alarm.
Returns a list of alarms with filter alarmName like Equipment with impact greater than 0 and severity equals major. The list will contain the objectFullName of each resulting alarm.

Returns a list of alarms with filter set (severity is either critical, major, warning and impact > 0 and implicityCleared is set to true . The list will contain the objectFullName of each resulting alarm.
